gory:Birds of the Atlantic Ocean]]\n[[Category:Birds of the Indian Ocean]]\n[[Category:Birds of the Pacific Ocean]]\n[[Category:Pantropical fauna]]\n[[Category:Least concern biota of Asia]]\n[[Category:Least concern biota of Oceania]]\n[[Category:Birds of Norfolk Island]]\n[[Category:Birds described in 1766|sooty tern]]\n", "name_user": "Rjwilmsi", "label": "safe", "comment": "Journal cites:, templated 2 journal cites", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sooty_tern"}
